摄影指导：GIUSEPPE ROTUNND, A.I.C.A.S.C

34
00:04:32,543 --> 00:04:36,827
造型设计：罗伯特・E・霍华德

35
00:04:37,482 --> 00:04:41,963
编剧：Clive Exton
乔治・麦克唐纳・弗雷泽

36
00:05:03,744 --> 00:05:07,013
制片：CHRISTIAN FERRY

37
00:05:08,043 --> 00:05:11,272
导演：理查德・弗莱舍

38
00:05:33,942 --> 00:05:37,306
Varna, where is the Lord of Hyrkania?
瓦尔纳，赫卡尼亚君主在哪里？

39
00:05:37,842 --> 00:05:39,831
He has not come, Highness.
他没有来，汉斯。

40
00:05:40,109 --> 00:05:43,234
He should be here
for the destruction of the talisman.
他应该在这儿
为了这毁灭性的神器

41
00:05:44,376 --> 00:05:48,399
But we cannot delay.
We will proceed without him.
但是我们不能拖延
即使没有他也要继续进行

42
00:06:14,077 --> 00:06:16,737
O God of the high Gods...
上帝啊!崇高的上帝啊……

43
00:06:17,344 --> 00:06:21,970
behold the talisman with which
you created the world and all things.
看你创造世界和所有事物的神器

44
00:06:30,112 --> 00:06:31,702
O God of Gods...
上帝啊上帝……

45
00:06:32,545 --> 00:06:35,170
it has become too powerful for us...
它将变得过于强大而使我们无法控制……

46
00:06:35,946 --> 00:06:39,742
and we must destroy it
before it destroys the world.
在它毁灭世界之前我们必须摧毁它

47
00:06:57,214 --> 00:07:00,737
Forgive us now
as we send it out of the light...
原谅我们
我们将让它离开光芒……

48
00:07:00,813 --> 00:07:03,143
from which it draws its power...
因为光芒能使它获得力量……

49
00:07:04,047 --> 00:07:06,513
into eternal darkness.
我们要使它进入永恒的黑暗之中。

50
00:07:19,748 --> 00:07:21,112
Forgive us.
原谅我们

51
00:09:31,456 --> 00:09:32,683
Come on.
来吧

52
00:09:54,624 --> 00:09:56,647
So this can make worlds...
它可以创造世界……

53
00:09:58,191 --> 00:10:01,021
or shatter them by storm and earthquake.
但也可以制造风暴和地震毁灭世界

54
00:10:03,791 --> 00:10:05,485
Have it lifted out.
把它抬出来

55
00:10:05,558 --> 00:10:06,956
Lift it out!
抬出来!

56
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,821
Touch it.
触摸它一下

57
00:11:38,197 --> 00:11:41,425
So it is true. Only women may touch it.
证明这是正确的，只有女人可以碰它。

58
00:11:43,865 --> 00:11:45,194
The cover.
盖起来

59
00:11:54,865 --> 00:11:56,229
Take it out.
抬出去

60
00:12:07,866 --> 00:12:11,230
Great queen,
what shall we do with the prisoners?
伟大的女王
我们应该怎么处置囚犯?

61
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:24,098
- No!
- No!
不!
不!

62
00:12:50,769 --> 00:12:51,860
Come.
跟我来

63
00:13:15,237 --> 00:13:16,430
Horses.
备马

64
00:15:20,211 --> 00:15:22,074
The talisman's stolen.
神器被偷人走了

65
00:15:23,711 --> 00:15:25,973
Must destroy the talisman.
必须毁坏这个神器

66
00:15:28,178 --> 00:15:31,201
We must find my sister. Take me.
我们必须找到我的妹妹，请带我走

67
00:15:31,912 --> 00:15:35,571
I know where she is. Please.
我知道她在哪儿，拜托了

68
00:16:10,680 --> 00:16:12,044
Magnificent.
很好

69
00:16:20,882 --> 00:16:23,780
You have nothing more to learn, Sonja.
这里没有东西可以供你学习了，桑妮亚

70
00:16:26,481 --> 00:16:30,414
You are the master of the master.
你非常优秀

71
00:16:31,616 --> 00:16:33,809
Never have I seen your equal.
你是无可匹敌的

72
00:16:48,250 --> 00:16:51,808
You must learn to like men a little better.
你必须学会对男人好一点

73
00:16:52,884 --> 00:16:54,747
They are not all evil.
他们并不是所有都是邪恶的

74
00:16:55,417 --> 00:16:58,577
We must judge by our own experience,
Grand Master.
我们必须根据我们的经验判断
长老

75
00:16:58,650 --> 00:16:59,809
I know.
我知道

76
00:17:00,950 --> 00:17:04,780
But in life, all is not swordplay.
但人并不是为了剑术而活着

77
00:17:06,017 --> 00:17:09,780
Hatred of men in a lovely young woman...
在一个美丽的年轻女子憎恨男人时……

78
00:17:11,118 --> 00:17:13,141
it could be your downfall.
它会令你垮台

79
00:17:14,918 --> 00:17:17,407
I don't hate all men, Grand Master.
我并不恨所有的男人，长老

80
00:17:18,419 --> 00:17:22,215
That would have been music to my ears
30 years ago.
那是30年前我听到的声音

81
00:17:22,985 --> 00:17:24,076
Come.
来吧

82
00:17:24,952 --> 00:17:29,214
A great swordsman
must have a great sword.
一个杰出的剑客必须有一把好剑

83
00:17:43,186 --> 00:17:44,379
Choose.
挑选吧

84
00:17:45,020 --> 00:17:47,542
A gift from the Grand Master.
作为长老给你的礼物

85
00:17:59,621 --> 00:18:00,780
Sonja.
桑妮亚

86
00:18:03,288 --> 00:18:05,151
What is it, Red Sonja?
怎么了？桑妮亚

87
00:18:34,290 --> 00:18:36,313
I'm looking for Red Sonja.
我在寻找桑妮亚

88
00:18:50,757 --> 00:18:53,552
- I am Sonja.
- Your sister's dying.
我是桑妮亚
你姐姐快要死了

89
00:18:56,358 --> 00:18:58,119
I'll take you to her.
我带你去见她

90
00:19:53,561 --> 00:19:54,686
Varna.
瓦尔纳

91
00:20:02,429 --> 00:20:03,759
Thank God.
谢天谢地

92
00:20:04,629 --> 00:20:06,527
I've lived long enough.
我终于坚持活到现在了

93
00:20:08,362 --> 00:20:10,225
The talisman's stolen.
神器被偷了

94
00:20:11,196 --> 00:20:13,855
All the priests massacred.
所有的神父被屠杀

95
00:20:14,996 --> 00:20:18,121
- We fought...
- Rest, Varna. Later we can talk.
我们要战斗
休息一下，瓦尔纳，我们可以晚点再说

96
00:20:18,663 --> 00:20:20,958
There's no time. Listen.
没有时间了，听着

97
00:20:23,263 --> 00:20:26,025
The talisman has terrible power...
这个神器有着恐怖的力量……

98
00:20:27,264 --> 00:20:29,253
which grows in the light.
它随着光照而成长

99
00:20:31,963 --> 00:20:36,191
In 13 days it could destroy the world...
它会在13天内毁灭世界……

100
00:20:37,164 --> 00:20:41,153
by storm and earthquake.
利用风暴和地震

101
00:20:48,764 --> 00:20:51,356
You must destroy the talisman, Sonja.
你必须毁坏这神器，桑妮亚

102
00:20:52,198 --> 00:20:56,426
Send it into darkness. Swear that you will.
你要对此发誓，使它进入永恒的黑暗之中

103
00:20:56,899 --> 00:20:58,126
I swear.
我发誓

104
00:20:59,365 --> 00:21:00,763
Who took it?
谁抢走了它?

105
00:21:01,632 --> 00:21:03,098
I don't know.
我不知道

106
00:21:05,066 --> 00:21:08,089
There was a woman with a gold mask.
是一个带金面具的女人

107
00:21:09,099 --> 00:21:10,360
Soldiers.
和她的士兵们

108
00:21:10,599 --> 00:21:13,463
Where did they take it? North? South?
他们带到哪儿去了?北方?南方?

109
00:21:24,467 --> 00:21:28,126
She's dead.
And the living have work to do.
她死了
我们活着的人做事去吧

110
00:21:31,901 --> 00:21:35,765
Her work, my work, is no concern of yours.
她的事，我的事，这与你没有关系

111
00:21:38,068 --> 00:21:40,863
- Who are you, anyway?
- My name is Kalidor.
告诉我你是谁?
我叫凯利多

112
00:21:41,668 --> 00:21:44,133
I befriended your sister, remember?
我照顾过你姐姐，记得么?

113
00:21:44,668 --> 00:21:46,463
I'm a friend of yours, too.
我也是你的朋友

114
00:21:46,535 --> 00:21:50,433
I thank you for what you did for my sister.
You will be rewarded.
谢谢你为我姐姐做的这些
我会给你赏金

115
00:21:50,668 --> 00:21:53,362
I'm no mercenary. Nobody pays me.
我不是为了钱，不需要付给我钱

116
00:21:54,002 --> 00:21:57,162
If I think somebody owes me something,
I take it.
如果我认为有人亏欠我什么
我会自己带走

117
00:22:40,971 --> 00:22:43,403
Someone is using the talisman.
有人在使用神器

118
00:22:45,305 --> 00:22:49,465
- What place is that?
- Hablok. It's a great city.
那是什么地方?
哈勃洛克，一个大城市

119
00:22:55,073 --> 00:22:56,834
Where are you going?
你要去哪里?

120
00:22:57,972 --> 00:22:59,165
Hablok.
哈勃洛克

121
00:23:00,872 --> 00:23:02,895
Wait. I'll come with you.
等一下，我和你一起去

122
00:23:03,373 --> 00:23:06,806
Why should you? It's no business of yours.
你为什么要去?这与你无关

123
00:23:07,173 --> 00:23:08,799
And neither am I.
你与我也没有关系

124
00:23:08,873 --> 00:23:11,203
You may be wrong on both counts.
你可能两个都弄错了

125
00:23:11,473 --> 00:23:14,928
I know you're a brave girl,
but danger is my trade.
我知道你是勇敢的女孩
但冒险是我的职业

126
00:23:15,673 --> 00:23:18,265
Then I'll learn it by myself.
我会自己学会这些

127
00:23:22,374 --> 00:23:24,567
Don't make me angry, Kalidor.
不要令我发怒，凯利多

128
00:23:25,274 --> 00:23:27,399
I don't need any man's help.
我不需要任何男人帮助

129
00:23:48,276 --> 00:23:52,402
Don't shake it, fool. Hold it steady!
Can you do nothing right?
不要晃动它，笨蛋，稳住它!
你能不能做点像样的?

130
00:23:52,876 --> 00:23:54,774
Still, you great idiot.
稳住，你个大笨蛋

131
00:23:55,643 --> 00:23:57,666
I'm trying, Your Highness.
我在努力，殿下

132
00:23:58,910 --> 00:24:02,808
Clumsy oaf. Stupid, dumb,
useless, selfish beast!
笨蛋，傻瓜，蠢货
没用的东西，讨厌的家伙!

133
00:24:03,043 --> 00:24:05,032
Quickly, come. Come to me.
快点，过来，到我这边来

134
00:24:05,243 --> 00:24:09,039
Don't give me orders, slave.
I'll have you hung by the heels.
不要对我发号施令，奴隶
我要给你戴上脚镣

135
00:24:09,277 --> 00:24:11,368
Anyway, it's too slippery.
不管它有多滑

136
00:24:11,644 --> 00:24:15,576
Do you want me to fall
in that boiling mud? You numskull.
你想让我掉入这些沸腾的泥浆中吗?
你这个笨蛋

137
00:24:16,278 --> 00:24:19,005
I'll try to swing it around. Now.
现在我要转动了

138
00:24:19,378 --> 00:24:21,775
- Hold still, boy.
- Boy?
站着不要动，小孩
小孩?

139
00:24:26,111 --> 00:24:29,010
Steady, Your Majesty. Steady.
稳住，陛下，稳住

140
00:24:48,546 --> 00:24:50,069
Jump off. Jump.
跳下来，跳

141
00:24:52,346 --> 00:24:54,073
What about me?
我怎么办?

142
00:24:54,146 --> 00:24:56,874
Get back here and stop playing the fool.
回到这儿，不要再做蠢事

143
00:24:57,914 --> 00:25:01,074
I hear and obey, master of the world.
I'm coming.
我听你的，世界的主
我来了

144
00:25:30,115 --> 00:25:33,343
Lucky for you that this person came along.
向前来的这个人，你真幸运

145
00:25:34,083 --> 00:25:36,605
Reward her, and tell her who I am.
奖赏给她，告诉她我是谁

146
00:25:38,749 --> 00:25:42,739
His Royal Highness, the Prince Tarn,
Great Lord of Hablok...
他是塔纳王子
伟大的哈勃洛克君主

147
00:25:43,816 --> 00:25:46,146
keeper of the spotless throne...
保持纯洁的王位

148
00:25:46,216 --> 00:25:48,739
great elephant who fertilizes the world
with his...
像大象一样高大，他肥沃大地用他的……

149
00:25:48,817 --> 00:25:51,045
I've told you not to say that.
我告诉过你不要说那些

150
00:25:51,316 --> 00:25:54,010
Do it again, and I'll have you impaled.
下次再这样我会把你钉在桩上

151
00:25:56,250 --> 00:25:58,478
Well, reward her, fool.
很好，奖赏给她，笨蛋

152
00:26:09,818 --> 00:26:13,615
From the look of your kingdom, Prince,
you need this more than I do.
从你的王国看，王子
你比我更需要这个

153
00:26:17,452 --> 00:26:19,179
Did she address me?
她在跟我说话么?

154
00:26:20,752 --> 00:26:22,240
What happened?
发生了什么事?

155
00:26:22,518 --> 00:26:25,212
Queen Gedren attacked us
is what happened.
就是戈登女王在攻击我们

156
00:26:25,286 --> 00:26:28,218
Gedren? Queen Gedren?
戈登?戈登女王?

157
00:26:28,618 --> 00:26:30,084
That's right.
对

158
00:26:30,852 --> 00:26:35,285
She knocked down half the city with her
new weapon and demanded our surrender.
她用她的新武器攻下了我们半座城池
并且要求我们投降

159
00:26:35,352 --> 00:26:36,978
My army ran away.
我的军队跑了

160
00:26:37,653 --> 00:26:39,812
Do they want to live forever?
难道他们以为那样会活长一点?

161
00:26:39,886 --> 00:26:42,011
I refused to surrender.
我绝不投降

162
00:26:42,586 --> 00:26:45,075
So she knocked down the other half.
她又攻下了另一半

163
00:26:45,820 --> 00:26:49,480
Falkon, since everyone is dead
or run away...
法拉肯，自从所有人死了或跑了……

164
00:26:49,887 --> 00:26:52,512
you shall escort me
to the mountains tomorrow.
你明天必须护送我到山上去

165
00:26:52,587 --> 00:26:54,519
I shall raise a new army...
我要建立一支新的军队

166
00:26:54,587 --> 00:26:57,985
and crush this upstart Gedren underfoot.
并且击败戈登，将她踩在脚下

167
00:26:58,687 --> 00:27:01,415
Where can I find her, this Queen Gedren?
在哪儿我能找到她，这个戈登女王?

168
00:27:01,687 --> 00:27:04,381
In Burkubane, the land of eternal night.
在布拉库班，一块黑暗之地

169
00:27:04,455 --> 00:27:05,785
How do I get there?
我可以如何去哪里?

170
00:27:05,855 --> 00:27:09,878
There's a long scenic way, and there's
the short way through Brytag's toll road.
远路是穿过景色优美的地带过去，
近路是穿过布拉塔格大门过去

171
00:27:09,955 --> 00:27:13,046
I'll take Brytag's toll road.
Which way is that?
我想穿过布拉塔格大门去
怎么走?

172
00:27:14,189 --> 00:27:17,087
Straight north from here.
You can't miss it.
一直向北走
你不会迷路的

173
00:27:18,189 --> 00:27:19,984
But it's worth a try.
但这值得一试

174
00:27:21,988 --> 00:27:24,887
Ask the woman
if she wishes to join my army.
告诉这个女人
如果她愿意加入我的军队

175
00:27:25,456 --> 00:27:27,547
We'll probably need a cook.
我们可能会需要厨师

176
00:27:27,689 --> 00:27:30,814
Your Highness is too kind,
but I travel alone.
殿下你太友善了
但是我喜欢独行

177
00:27:32,190 --> 00:27:36,020
Dismiss the woman, Falkon.
I shall dine in an hour.
叫这个女人退下，法拉肯
我一个小时后将要吃饭

178
00:27:42,156 --> 00:27:44,486
May I give you a word of advice?
我可以给你一字忠告么?

179
00:27:44,590 --> 00:27:48,023
Put him over your knee
and beat some manners into him.
把他放到你膝盖上
礼貌的敲他几下

180
00:27:50,091 --> 00:27:52,683
You wouldn't happen to have a tablecloth,
would you?
你没有马鞍
需要么?

181
00:28:46,561 --> 00:28:49,084
Brytag, come down and open the gate.
布拉塔格，把门放下并打开

182
00:28:49,527 --> 00:28:51,323
Not so fast, redhead.
没这么快，红发人

183
00:28:52,328 --> 00:28:55,192
I'm up here
where I can get a better look at you.
抬起头来
那样能看你清楚一点

184
00:28:55,261 --> 00:28:57,591
I have no time to waste, Brytag.
我没有时间了，布拉塔格

185
00:28:58,261 --> 00:29:01,159
I have plenty. Come up, I say.
我有的是时间，头起头来

186
00:29:48,431 --> 00:29:50,761
- Come here, wench.
- Why should I?
过来吧，姑娘
我为什么要过来?

187
00:29:54,398 --> 00:29:57,660
Because I am Brytag. This is my land.
因为我是布拉塔格，这是我的地盘

188
00:29:58,731 --> 00:30:01,289
All that pass through pay me tribute.
所有要通过的人须给我贡物

189
00:30:01,365 --> 00:30:04,058
- How much, Brytag?
- Who mentioned money?
要多少?布拉塔格
谁说要钱的?

190
00:30:04,965 --> 00:30:06,556
Tribute, I said.
我说了，贡物

191
00:30:07,232 --> 00:30:09,755
The tender kind all women pay to Brytag.
把女人温柔的东西给布拉塔格

192
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:21,156
Suppose I don't.
我想我不会

193
00:30:21,533 --> 00:30:25,397
Suppose, instead, I open up
that great fat belly of yours.
相反的，我想将你开膛破肚

194
00:30:29,834 --> 00:30:31,323
You hear that?
你听到她说什么了么?

195
00:30:31,767 --> 00:30:34,233
She's going to open up my great...
她要切开我的……

196
00:30:36,601 --> 00:30:40,192
Woman, I have fought 177 men.
女人，我过去和177个男子战斗过

197
00:30:40,468 --> 00:30:43,434
Only one survives, and he has got no legs.
只有一个生还，但他失去了胳膊

198
00:30:43,868 --> 00:30:46,096
You dare to mock at Brytag?
你胆敢取笑我布拉塔格?

199
00:30:46,968 --> 00:30:48,763
That takes no daring.
有什么不敢的

200
00:30:52,435 --> 00:30:56,390
But when I've killed you,
will your warriors let me go unharmed?
但当我杀了你
你的武士能不能让我平安过去?

201
00:30:56,802 --> 00:30:58,995
When you've killed me?
当你杀了我?

202
00:31:01,136 --> 00:31:05,626
When this wench has killed me,
you will let her go unharmed, won't you?
当这个女人杀了我
你可以让她平安过去，明白么?

203
00:31:06,069 --> 00:31:07,126
Aye.
好

204
00:31:12,903 --> 00:31:13,960
See?
看?

205
00:31:17,603 --> 00:31:18,933
So, wench.
就这样，女人

206
00:31:23,337 --> 00:31:26,394
I'm gonna feed your eyes
to the birds, red hair.
我要把你的眼睛喂鸟，红发女人

207
00:31:26,637 --> 00:31:28,535
I don't need eyes to find you.
我不需要眼睛找你

208
00:31:28,604 --> 00:31:31,093
I can smell you at a hundred paces.
一百步内我能闻到你

209
00:32:21,174 --> 00:32:24,334
I will tell the future in your entrails,
red woman.
我会在你内脏告诉你将来的事，
红发女人

210
00:32:24,674 --> 00:32:27,539
I know my future. You have none.
我知道我的将来，而你没有

211
00:33:17,844 --> 00:33:19,333
Hold on, Sonja.
坚持住，桑妮亚

212
00:33:28,212 --> 00:33:29,734
Sonja, come on.
桑妮亚，来吧

213
00:33:48,146 --> 00:33:49,407
Look out!
看外面

214
00:34:10,881 --> 00:34:12,642
This way. Follow me!
这边，跟着我!

215
00:34:13,581 --> 00:34:15,945
- Get away. Go!
- What about you?
离开，走!
你怎么办?

216
00:34:16,014 --> 00:34:17,775
I can hold them. Go!
我可以坚持住，走!

217
00:34:20,448 --> 00:34:22,277
Hurry! Stop them!
快!拦住他们!

218
00:34:58,050 --> 00:34:59,812
Release me, ruffian!
放开我，恶棍

219
00:35:00,051 --> 00:35:01,710
Release me, I say!
我说了，放开我!

220
00:35:03,251 --> 00:35:05,910
- Tell us where it is.
- I'll have your head for this!
告诉我这是哪儿
我带你们到这儿!

221
00:35:05,984 --> 00:35:07,450
Don't be shy.
不要害怕

222
00:35:09,951 --> 00:35:12,281
The gold, boy. Where's the gold?
黄金，小孩，黄金在哪儿?

223
00:35:12,984 --> 00:35:15,008
There is no gold, ruffian.
这儿没有黄金，恶棍

224
00:35:20,418 --> 00:35:23,044
I tell you, I have no gold!
我告诉你，我没有黄金!

225
00:35:24,285 --> 00:35:28,650
You have fine raiment, boy,
almost as resplendent as mine.
你有华丽的服饰，小孩
几乎和我们差不多华丽

226
00:35:29,719 --> 00:35:32,049
And you expect me to believe
you're penniless?
我们会相信你身无分文么?

227
00:35:32,120 --> 00:35:36,348
I'll have you know, villain,
I am Prince Tarn of Hablok.
我要你们知道，恶棍
我是哈勃洛克王子

228
00:35:36,719 --> 00:35:40,208
My subjects will see
to your punishment for this.
我会使你们为此受到惩罚

229
00:35:40,786 --> 00:35:44,879
And a grievous punishment it will be,
impertinent oaf!
会有严重的惩罚
无理的呆子!

230
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:46,609
Your subjects?
你的麻烦?

231
00:35:46,987 --> 00:35:49,248
My kingdom is greater than yours.
我的王国比你们的大

232
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:51,287
And I have but four.
虽然我只排行第四

233
00:35:54,454 --> 00:35:55,714
Pull him!
拉他过来!

234
00:37:02,525 --> 00:37:06,082
- Are you all right, your sovereign Majesty?
- Yes, clumsy oaf.
你没事吧，王子殿下
是的，笨蛋

235
00:37:07,091 --> 00:37:08,955
Why did you leave him?
你为什么不在他身边?

236
00:37:09,458 --> 00:37:11,424
We needed food. I went hunting.
我们需要食物，我打猎去了

237
00:37:11,492 --> 00:37:13,617
You could have taken him with you.
你可以让他跟你一起去

238
00:37:13,692 --> 00:37:16,715
Tell her, Falkon,
that I don't care for hunting.
告诉她，法拉肯
我不喜欢打猎

239
00:37:18,792 --> 00:37:20,917
He doesn't care for hunting.
他不喜欢打猎

240
00:37:50,628 --> 00:37:54,287
Treasure to the vaults,
prisoners to the dungeons.
珠宝放到金库里
囚犯押到地牢处

241
00:37:55,128 --> 00:37:57,993
Take the talisman back
to the Chamber of Lights.
把神器抬到有光的地方去

242
00:37:58,062 --> 00:37:59,823
Very well, my queen.
好的，我的女王

243
00:39:30,234 --> 00:39:33,758
Perhaps fewer candles...
或许一些蜡烛……

244
00:39:34,100 --> 00:39:36,430
would be advisable, Your Majesty.
是可取的，陛下

245
00:39:36,934 --> 00:39:37,991
Why?
为什么?

246
00:39:38,201 --> 00:39:41,633
The stronger the light, the greater
the power of the talisman grows.
光越强，神器的能量也会越强

247
00:39:41,701 --> 00:39:43,792
I want more light here, not less.
我要这儿更多的光，不是一点点

248
00:39:43,868 --> 00:39:47,562
But it is dangerously powerful already,
great queen.
但它已经有毁灭性的力量了
伟大的女王

249
00:39:47,635 --> 00:39:52,000
- Look what it did to Hablok.
- Yes. Very satisfying.
看它击败哈勃洛克
是的，非常满意

250
00:39:53,169 --> 00:39:56,692
But I want its full power
when we march against Toktyl, Ikol.
但我想要它全部的力量
当我们攻打塔克特，阿克罗时

251
00:39:56,768 --> 00:39:58,200
Its full power.
需要全部力量

252
00:39:58,269 --> 00:40:01,497
- It will be beyond our control, Majesty.
- Majesty!
那样它将使我们无法控制的，陛下
陛下!

253
00:40:01,569 --> 00:40:04,296
Enemies are approaching
the outer empire.
敌人接近了
在帝国外面

254
00:41:42,909 --> 00:41:45,898
It's the Prince of Hablok, Your Majesty...
是哈勃洛克的王子，陛下……

255
00:41:45,976 --> 00:41:47,908
with his army.
和他的军队

256
00:41:48,042 --> 00:41:49,269
Insects.
昆虫

257
00:41:53,942 --> 00:41:55,238
That girl.
那个女孩

258
00:41:57,810 --> 00:42:01,207
So she escaped the fire. How fortunate.
原来她从战斗中逃脱了，真是好运啊

259
00:42:02,476 --> 00:42:07,034
Ikol, I want her alive
without so much as a scratch on her skin.
阿克罗，我要她不受伤害的活着

260
00:42:07,676 --> 00:42:10,302
Shall I send out a small ambush party?
我们要派人去袭击他们么?

261
00:42:12,677 --> 00:42:13,700
No.
不

262
00:42:14,744 --> 00:42:17,539
We'll wait till they get a little closer.
我们等他们再靠近一点

263
00:42:33,945 --> 00:42:38,071
Burkubane, the land of perpetual night.
布拉库班，黑暗之地

264
00:42:38,212 --> 00:42:41,201
Falkon, proclaim my arrival...
法拉肯，宣布我们抵达……

265
00:42:41,346 --> 00:42:43,868
and the defiance of Queen Gedren.
并向戈登女王开战

266
00:42:44,212 --> 00:42:45,939
Sound your trumpet.
大声一点

267
00:42:46,479 --> 00:42:48,206
Keep quiet...
保持安静……

268
00:42:48,779 --> 00:42:51,370
at least till we find a way across.
至少等到我们找到进去的路

269
00:42:51,446 --> 00:42:55,379
Princes do not sneak in
on their enemies like thieves.
王子不能在敌人面前像贼一样

270
00:42:56,013 --> 00:42:58,808
You don't know
much about princes, do you?
你不知道很多关于王子的事，是么?

271
00:43:27,815 --> 00:43:30,043
You wait here with the horses.
你在这儿看着马

272
00:43:31,415 --> 00:43:34,279
I want to test this bridge first.
我先检查一下这座桥

273
00:43:34,849 --> 00:43:36,542
Or whatever it is.
或者说是这类似桥的东西

274
00:44:15,718 --> 00:44:18,980
It looks safe enough.
We'll lead the horses across.
它看起来很安全
我们牵着马过去

275
00:44:22,085 --> 00:44:24,108
Now hear me, Gedren!
现在听我说，戈登!

276
00:44:24,185 --> 00:44:26,879
It is I, Prince Tarn of Hablok...
这就是我，哈勃洛克的王子……

277
00:44:26,952 --> 00:44:30,577
to revenge myself
on the tyrant of Burkubane.
为自己报仇
在粗暴的布拉库班身上

278
00:44:31,153 --> 00:44:34,608
Be quiet, you arrogant, ungrateful pup.
小声点，你太自大了，忘恩负义的家伙

279
00:44:35,419 --> 00:44:37,214
How dare you, woman?
你怎么害怕了，女人?

280
00:44:37,286 --> 00:44:39,218
I'll show you how I dare.
我让你看我有多害怕

281
00:44:39,286 --> 00:44:41,809
This should have been done long ago.
这是我很早之前就想做的

282
00:44:42,153 --> 00:44:45,517
No. If you must hit someone, then hit me.
不，如果你一定要打人，就打我吧

283
00:44:48,620 --> 00:44:50,779
You're not worth the effort, boy.
你没有这个能力，孩子

284
00:44:50,853 --> 00:44:52,944
Boy?
孩子?

285
00:44:53,020 --> 00:44:55,816
Yes, boy. You'll never be anything else...
是的，孩子，你将失去所有除非……

286
00:44:55,888 --> 00:44:59,479
till you learn gratitude
and self-sacrifice, like Falkon.
直到你学会感激
和自我牺牲，像法拉肯那样

287
00:44:59,687 --> 00:45:01,312
He's a real man.
他是真男人

288
00:45:08,787 --> 00:45:12,982
She didn't mean it, my prince.
She doesn't know your fine qualities.
她不是这个意思，王子
她不知道你是上等人

289
00:45:30,823 --> 00:45:32,550
Take that, ruffian.
看招，恶棍

290
00:45:46,524 --> 00:45:48,422
Take that, you ruffian.
看招，你是恶棍

291
00:46:03,591 --> 00:46:05,420
Practicing, Highness?
在练功，王子?

292
00:46:05,725 --> 00:46:09,317
I thought princes did everything so well,
they wouldn't need to.
我想王子既然每一件事都做得这么好
应该不需要别人帮忙的

293
00:46:09,825 --> 00:46:12,553
I was disarmed by those ruffians
the other day.
那天这些恶棍来时我没带武器

294
00:46:12,626 --> 00:46:15,751
I noticed. So? It needn't be fatal.
我注意到了，所以?但这不是致命的

295
00:46:16,192 --> 00:46:18,488
I am disarmed. Kill me. Come on.
我现在也没带武器，杀了我，来吧

296
00:46:19,425 --> 00:46:20,652
Come on!
来吧!

297
00:46:29,260 --> 00:46:32,021
You're meant to be
using your sword. Remember?
你应该用你的剑，记住了么?

298
00:46:39,660 --> 00:46:41,320
Simple, isn't it?
很简单，是不是?

299
00:46:41,793 --> 00:46:44,021
But it's not in the rule book.
但这不是书上的规则

300
00:46:44,094 --> 00:46:47,356
You see, fencing and fighting
are two different things.
你看，击剑和好战是两种不同的事

301
00:46:47,860 --> 00:46:50,019
You need to learn them both.
两样你都需要学

302
00:47:01,462 --> 00:47:05,485
Will you teach me to fence and to fight?
你可以教我击剑和战斗?

303
00:47:07,095 --> 00:47:08,618
If you please?
求你了?

304
00:47:13,396 --> 00:47:15,157
Spoken like a prince.
这样说才有点像王子

305
00:47:19,596 --> 00:47:23,221
You were disarmed
because you hold the hilt too tight.
你兵器脱手了
是因为你握剑柄太牢了

306
00:47:23,463 --> 00:47:25,429
Grip gently. See?
轻轻的握住，看到了么?

307
00:47:29,230 --> 00:47:31,593
Gently. I see. Like this?
轻轻的，我看，就像这样?

308
00:47:33,264 --> 00:47:35,287
Your Highness learns fast.
殿下你学得真快

309
00:47:36,197 --> 00:47:39,755
I think we'll continue
your fencing lessons another time.
我想下次我们应该继续你的击剑课程

310
00:47:41,131 --> 00:47:42,926
We've an early start.
我们尽快开始

311
00:47:43,464 --> 00:47:45,260
You are very beautiful.
你非常漂亮

312
00:47:45,331 --> 00:47:48,888
When I am king of Hablok,
I shall have you at my court.
当我成为哈勃洛克国王时
我可以将我的宫殿给你

313
00:47:49,797 --> 00:47:52,127
You will? My, the honor.
你真这样想么?我很感激你

314
00:47:53,532 --> 00:47:55,760
I may even make you my queen.
我或许还可以让你成为我的皇后

315
00:47:56,198 --> 00:47:58,323
But I'm still young.
但我太年轻了

316
00:47:58,832 --> 00:48:00,661
We shall have to see.
我们以后再说

317
00:48:33,433 --> 00:48:36,558
They will reach
the Ithian Cavern tomorrow.
他们快到了
明天应该能到Ithian洞穴

318
00:48:36,634 --> 00:48:39,430
We must force them to take shelter there.
我们必须派人保护那儿

319
00:48:40,168 --> 00:48:42,794
The killing machine will do the rest.
这个杀人机器也许可以帮我们完成这个任务

320
00:48:42,868 --> 00:48:45,299
Yes. They'll make fine fish food.
是的，他们将成为它的美餐

321
00:48:46,902 --> 00:48:48,561
But not the girl.
但不包括那个女孩

322
00:48:48,902 --> 00:48:52,561
I want that beauty here with me.
See to it that she is spared.
我想这么美丽的人伴在我身边
看到她就这么死了有点舍不得

323
00:48:53,968 --> 00:48:56,832
I'll do my best, my queen.
我会尽量做得最好的，女王

324
00:48:57,369 --> 00:49:00,392
The machine is difficult to control.
但这个机器很难控制

325
00:49:00,469 --> 00:49:03,958
One cannot guarantee
that something will not go wrong.
不能保证万一出现什么问题

326
00:49:05,769 --> 00:49:09,065
If it does, you will be its next victim.
如果这样，你将会成为下一个受害者

327
00:49:21,304 --> 00:49:25,168
The talisman, Ikol. We need a storm.
把神器带来，阿克罗，我们需要风暴

328
00:49:26,703 --> 00:49:28,101
A little one.
小一点的

329
00:49:40,138 --> 00:49:42,070
We should be out in the storm.
我们需要使风暴停止

330
00:49:43,105 --> 00:49:45,094
Why? This is shelter, isn't it?
为什么?我们可以在这里躲避它，不是么?

331
00:49:45,172 --> 00:49:49,332
I haven't got time to shelter.
I've four days left to find the talisman.
我没有时间去避难
我只有4天时间去找神器

332
00:49:51,772 --> 00:49:54,397
Besides, something drove us in here...
而且，有人往这边来了

333
00:49:54,739 --> 00:49:56,534
every bit of the way.
每一条路上

334
00:49:57,872 --> 00:50:00,498
I noticed it, but I'm not complaining.
我知道这些，但我不是抱怨

335
00:50:03,840 --> 00:50:05,271
Where's Tarn?
王子在哪里?

336
00:50:06,806 --> 00:50:10,068
He promised not to wander.
Dry off, I'll go find him.
他说过不会走开的
你在这儿烘干衣服，我去找他

337
00:50:16,240 --> 00:50:17,729
Look at this.
看看这个

338
00:50:24,474 --> 00:50:26,963
It must be the biggest in the world.
这一定是世界上最大的

339
00:50:32,441 --> 00:50:35,464
Could be fake.
There's a lot of bad stuff around.
可能是假的
这附近有很多脏东西

340
00:50:35,542 --> 00:50:38,099
This pearl can rebuild Hablok...
这颗珍珠能用来重建哈勃洛克……

341
00:50:38,175 --> 00:50:41,300
fill its treasury, buy me an army.
用它填满国库，用来建一支军队

342
00:50:42,176 --> 00:50:43,505
Dig it out!
挖走它

343
00:50:43,575 --> 00:50:46,474
Your Highness,
it may belong to somebody.
殿下
它可能属于某人所有

344
00:50:47,109 --> 00:50:49,507
It does, and he wants it now!
是的，并且他马上要!

345
00:50:50,909 --> 00:50:52,034
Yeah.
好吧

346
00:50:58,676 --> 00:51:00,574
Use your dagger, fool!
用你的匕首，笨蛋!

347
00:51:21,745 --> 00:51:23,142
What are you doing?
你在做什么?

348
00:51:23,211 --> 00:51:25,939
Falkon, Highness, look at the water!
法拉肯，殿下，看很多水!

349
00:51:26,978 --> 00:51:29,876
Come on. Put your back into it.
来吧，把你力气都用进去

350
00:51:30,378 --> 00:51:33,572
It won't budge.
Maybe it wasn't meant to come out.
它不会动
或许它不想出来

351
00:51:33,912 --> 00:51:36,935
The water is rising.
You must get out of here.
水在上涨
你必须离开这里

352
00:51:47,479 --> 00:51:50,570
- This way! Make for the stairs!
- Come, my prince!
这边!往台阶那边去!
走，王子!

353
00:52:21,814 --> 00:52:23,973
- Get out of the water!
- Yes.
离开水!
是

354
00:52:26,215 --> 00:52:28,306
Climb up here, my prince.
从这儿往上爬，王子

355
00:53:01,684 --> 00:53:02,809
Tarn!
王子!

356
00:53:04,217 --> 00:53:06,081
I'm coming, my prince!
我来了，王子!

357
00:53:16,118 --> 00:53:17,311
Let go!
我们走!

358
00:53:46,320 --> 00:53:47,785
Where is she?
她哪儿去了?

359
00:55:28,626 --> 00:55:30,990
I can't kill it! It's a machine!
我杀不了它，它是机器!

360
00:55:47,561 --> 00:55:49,686
Sonja, we have to blind it!
桑妮亚，我们需要把它弄瞎

361
00:55:50,894 --> 00:55:52,689
It's our only chance!
这是我们唯一的机会

362
00:56:22,197 --> 00:56:24,788
Falkon, get out! It can't see!
法拉肯，快出去!它看不见了!

363
00:57:12,732 --> 00:57:15,290
There. Keep it covered.
这里，遮盖起来

364
00:57:17,233 --> 00:57:19,256
Why have you been following me?
你为什么跟着我?

365
00:57:19,333 --> 00:57:21,799
To see that you reach the talisman safely.
看你安全到达神器处

366
00:57:21,867 --> 00:57:23,026
Why?
为什么?

367
00:57:23,366 --> 00:57:26,526
I have to be sure
that the talisman is destroyed.
我肯定那个神器是毁灭性的

368
00:57:27,134 --> 00:57:29,622
Centuries ago, the high lords of Arcadia...
一个世纪前，阿卡迪亚的高贵的君主……

369
00:57:29,700 --> 00:57:32,633
had entrusted the talisman
to the priestesses...
把神器交给女祭司……

370
00:57:32,700 --> 00:57:35,064
because only women may touch it.
因为只有女人能碰它

371
00:57:35,401 --> 00:57:38,458
But to guard it,
or to destroy it if need be...
但要保护它，或者如果需要破坏它的话……

372
00:57:39,035 --> 00:57:41,523
is still the duty of the High Lord.
仍然是高贵的君主的职责

373
00:57:41,701 --> 00:57:43,758
You? The High Lord?
你?高贵的君主?

374
00:57:45,601 --> 00:57:48,897
I was coming to the temple
to see the talisman destroyed...
我是来神殿看神器被销毁……

375
00:57:48,968 --> 00:57:51,264
when I found your sister dying...
当我看到你姐姐死亡的时候……

376
00:57:51,335 --> 00:57:53,961
and learnt that the talisman
had been stolen.
并且知道神器被偷走了

377
00:57:54,569 --> 00:57:56,432
So she guided me to you.
所以她指引我去找你

378
00:57:56,502 --> 00:57:59,025
Why didn't you tell me who you were?
为什么你不告诉我你是谁?

379
00:58:00,535 --> 00:58:03,093
You didn't seem to want a man's help.
你好像从来不要男人的帮助

380
00:58:03,169 --> 00:58:06,260
But you needed it,
so that's why I followed you.
但你需要它
这就是我跟着你的原因

381
00:58:06,869 --> 00:58:09,700
I had to be sure you reached the talisman.
我得确保你能安全到达神器所在地

382
00:58:10,536 --> 00:58:11,695
I see.
我看

383
00:58:12,770 --> 00:58:15,964
I misunderstood.
I thought you had another reason.
我误解了
我认为你有别的目的

384
00:58:23,804 --> 00:58:24,996
I did.
是的

385
00:58:35,004 --> 00:58:37,834
No. I'm under a vow.
不，我发过誓

386
00:58:40,938 --> 00:58:44,632
No man may have me
unless he has beaten me in a fair fight.
没有人能得到我除非他能打败我

387
00:58:49,972 --> 00:58:54,098
So the only man that can have you
is one who has tried to kill you.
也就是说只有设法杀了你的男人才能得到你

388
00:58:56,406 --> 00:58:57,872
That's logic.
很有逻辑性

389
00:59:26,107 --> 00:59:30,005
If you yield only to a conqueror,
then prepare to be conquered.
如果你只屈服于征服者
那就整备被征服

390
00:59:41,942 --> 00:59:45,102
Don't be a fool. I don't want to kill you.
别这么傻，我没想过要杀你

391
00:59:45,742 --> 00:59:46,935
Try it.
试过再说

392
00:59:55,276 --> 00:59:56,536
Come on.
来吧

393
01:00:06,010 --> 01:00:08,703
Keep it down over there.
We're trying to sleep.
到那边打去
我们正在睡觉

394
01:00:29,212 --> 01:00:30,871
Are you all right?
你没事吧?

395
01:00:31,111 --> 01:00:34,100
Yes, Prince. We were just practicing.
是的，王子，我们只是在练习而已

396
01:00:35,212 --> 01:00:36,838
Then let me down!
放我下去

397
01:00:44,213 --> 01:00:45,543
Thank you.
谢谢

398
01:02:08,717 --> 01:02:10,809
Why does she fight so hard?
为什么她打得这么激烈?

399
01:02:11,418 --> 01:02:13,384
She doesn't want to win.
她没想过要赢

400
01:03:52,190 --> 01:03:56,089
Gedren's army.
Another kingdom enslaved.
戈登的军队
又一个王国被征服了

401
01:04:25,559 --> 01:04:28,025
The talisman! We must find a way in.
那个神器!我们必须找到一条路进去

402
01:04:41,727 --> 01:04:43,488
We'll have to climb.
我们攀爬进去

403
01:04:47,827 --> 01:04:49,816
Three of us should go in.
我们中3个人必须去

404
01:04:49,894 --> 01:04:53,520
Who'll stand guard this doorway,
the post of danger?
谁可以留下来守这道门
这个危险的工作?

405
01:04:54,394 --> 01:04:56,451
- Falkon?
- Me? Here?
法拉肯?
我?这里?

406
01:04:56,528 --> 01:04:59,460
I don't know what's coming out that door.
No, I am going up.
我不知道出了这道门会发生什么事
不，我能力不够

407
01:04:59,528 --> 01:05:00,721
Coward!
懦夫

408
01:05:01,028 --> 01:05:03,256
I'll take my chances in there.
我留下来

409
01:05:03,661 --> 01:05:05,457
And I have to go in.
我继续往前

410
01:05:17,263 --> 01:05:18,592
I'll stay.
我留下来吧

411
01:05:26,763 --> 01:05:28,752
Take care, Your Highness.
小心点，殿下

412
01:05:45,331 --> 01:05:46,627
Thank you.
谢谢

413
01:07:08,970 --> 01:07:10,993
Tomorrow, I start my diet.
明天，我要开始减肥

414
01:07:15,803 --> 01:07:18,531
Majesty, the talisman
is almost beyond control.
陛下，神器已经快无法控制了

415
01:07:18,604 --> 01:07:21,161
We must bury it in the dark
before it is too late!
我们必须把它埋在暗处
现在做还不晚!

416
01:07:21,237 --> 01:07:25,034
It'll be buried when I have no further use
for it, and that time is not yet.
它会在对我们没用之后再埋掉
那时也还不迟

417
01:07:25,104 --> 01:07:29,002
But it will kill us all!
O God, Majesty, what do you want?
但它会杀了我们!
哦，天哪，陛下，你想干什么?

418
01:07:29,304 --> 01:07:32,827
Our vaults are brimming with gold.
Great states live in terror of us!
我们的金库已充满黄金
就算是最强大的国家现在也害怕我们

419
01:07:32,904 --> 01:07:35,496
- What more is there?
- The world, Ikol!
我们该知足了?
世界，阿克罗!

420
01:07:35,805 --> 01:07:38,999
Today we took another piece
of the city of Toktyl.
今天我们只是拿下塔克特城的另一部分

421
01:07:39,072 --> 01:07:42,765
But I have wider claims
and the talisman will enforce them!
但现在我又有更大的欲望，
而神器能使我的欲望实现!

422
01:07:43,838 --> 01:07:46,430
Madness. There will be no world.
疯了，世界将毁灭了

423
01:07:47,505 --> 01:07:50,198
There will be no world.
世界将毁灭了

424
01:08:49,842 --> 01:08:53,740
We must find the talisman.
Only I can touch it, remember.
我们必须找到神器
记住，只有我能碰它

425
01:08:55,109 --> 01:08:59,337
You take that way, I'll go the other way.
Falkon, you take the center.
你走那条路，我走这条路
法拉肯，你走中间那条

426
01:09:10,810 --> 01:09:12,868
How's the food around here?
身边怎么这么多食物?

427
01:09:13,911 --> 01:09:15,274
Who are you?
你是谁?

428
01:10:22,815 --> 01:10:25,338
- Look for the talisman.
- Yeah. Right.
去找神器
好的，马上去

429
01:10:46,617 --> 01:10:49,549
- Ikol, Gedren's black spider.
- You.
阿克罗，你这个戈登的爪牙
你是?

430
01:10:49,617 --> 01:10:52,139
Yes. Prince Tarn of Hablok:
对，我是哈勃洛克王子

431
01:10:52,216 --> 01:10:55,546
The city you blasted
with your filthy sorcery.
来自被你用肮脏的巫术破坏的那座城市

432
01:10:59,483 --> 01:11:02,416
So the royal brat hasn't learnt his lesson.
看来王子你还没吸取教训

433
01:11:03,217 --> 01:11:05,012
Out of my way, child.
离我远点，小毛孩

434
01:11:05,984 --> 01:11:09,042
So that you can desert,
like the thief you are?
你以为你能像小偷一样逃跑吗?

435
01:11:10,451 --> 01:11:12,042
With my gold?
带着我的黄金?

436
01:11:12,884 --> 01:11:14,373
Hablok's gold?
哈勃洛克的黄金?

437
01:11:20,452 --> 01:11:24,009
Now that was unmannerly
of Your Highness...
现在你这个粗鲁的家伙……

438
01:11:24,619 --> 01:11:28,108
and rude little boys need correction...
没礼貌的小毛孩必须改过……

439
01:11:28,418 --> 01:11:31,612
if they're going to grow up into...
如果他们将你培养成为……

440
01:11:39,820 --> 01:11:43,582
I'm afraid Your Highness' growth
is going to be stunted permanently.
我恐怕你们的王室将就此灭亡

441
01:11:48,620 --> 01:11:51,950
Now, yield, Black Spider.
现在，投降吧，爪牙

442
01:12:40,390 --> 01:12:42,185
Where's Queen Gedren?
戈登女王在哪里?

443
01:12:42,257 --> 01:12:45,121
She's gone. I'm so glad that you've come.
她离开了。很高兴你的到来

444
01:12:47,690 --> 01:12:50,747
Please, will you protect me?
I'm so frightened.
你可以保护我么?
我很害怕

445
01:13:03,925 --> 01:13:07,289
Gedren! Where are you?
戈登!你在哪里?

446
01:13:09,491 --> 01:13:13,618
So the Prince of Hablok
honors us with his presence unwisely.
原来哈勃洛克的王子是这么没用的

447
01:13:13,992 --> 01:13:18,448
How many are with you?
Tell me! How many are with you?
和你一起来的有几个人?
告诉我!和你一起来的有几个人?

448
01:13:19,225 --> 01:13:22,090
- How many?
- Enough, Gedren!
有几个?
够了，戈登!

449
01:13:26,792 --> 01:13:29,883
Get back, or Hablok will need
an heir to the throne.
退后，不然我杀了哈勃洛克王子

450
01:13:29,959 --> 01:13:31,982
And your own throne, Gedren.
想办法保住你自己的王位吧，戈登

451
01:13:32,059 --> 01:13:36,015
Unless the talisman goes into the dark,
your whole kingdom will...
除非神器进入黑暗之处，
否则你的整个王国将……

452
01:13:40,426 --> 01:13:42,722
Prince, get Kalidor and Falkon.
王子，快到凯利多和法拉肯身边去

453
01:13:44,194 --> 01:13:46,524
There's a way behind the throne.
龙椅后面有条路

454
01:13:48,160 --> 01:13:50,422
The talisman, Gedren. Quickly!
交出神器，戈登，快!

455
01:13:50,894 --> 01:13:55,020
You are a fool.
We could have ruled the world together.
你想得太天真了
本来我们可以一起统治世界

456
01:13:55,095 --> 01:13:59,652
Now I shall rule alone,
and you will die for what you did to me.
但现在我将一个人统治了
你将因对我所做的这些而死

457
01:13:59,728 --> 01:14:01,160
What I did?
我做了什么?

458
01:14:01,629 --> 01:14:04,493
You slaughtered my parents like cattle.
你像杀牛一样样杀害我父母

459
01:14:04,562 --> 01:14:07,119
My brother, my sister!
我的兄弟，我的姐妹!

460
01:14:07,362 --> 01:14:10,090
Vermin! What were their lives
compared to this?
够了!跟我这相比那些算得了什么?

461
01:14:11,196 --> 01:14:14,719
You are mad!
The talisman will destroy you.
你这个疯子!
神器会杀死你

462
01:15:13,966 --> 01:15:15,693
Up here, Sonja.
上来，桑妮亚

463
01:15:17,633 --> 01:15:18,894
Up here.
上来

464
01:17:32,008 --> 01:17:35,907
Kalidor, Falkon, this way! Hurry!
凯利多，法拉肯，走这边!快!

465
01:18:04,377 --> 01:18:06,366
Down this hallway!
沿着这走廊走!

466
01:18:19,044 --> 01:18:21,169
Sonja. Over here.
桑妮亚，到这边来

467
01:18:34,445 --> 01:18:35,933
Falkon, help.
法拉肯，帮忙

468
01:18:50,646 --> 01:18:52,135
Prince Tarn, come back.
王子，回来

469
01:18:52,213 --> 01:18:55,771
I am here, Gedren. Death to all tyrants.
我在这里，戈登。我要杀死所有暴君

470
01:19:24,382 --> 01:19:26,143
Sonja, help me!
桑妮亚，快来帮我!

471
01:19:26,482 --> 01:19:27,913
I'm trapped!
我被压住了!

472
01:19:32,782 --> 01:19:35,771
Sonja! Behind you!
桑妮亚!小心你后面!

473
01:20:49,253 --> 01:20:51,014
I can't get through.
我通不过

474
01:20:53,854 --> 01:20:56,820
Falkon, pull her through. I'll hold the gate.
法拉肯，拉她过来。我来顶住门

475
01:21:59,424 --> 01:22:01,754
Follow me. This is the way out.
跟我走，这是出去的路

476
01:22:09,025 --> 01:22:10,548
How do you know, Highness?
你怎么知道的，殿下?

477
01:22:10,625 --> 01:22:13,318
Because this is the way
I came in, you clown.
因为我从这里进来的，笨蛋

478
01:22:25,226 --> 01:22:27,021
Here's the way through.
这里有路可以过去

479
01:22:27,092 --> 01:22:28,490
Go. Quickly!
走，快!

480
01:22:52,694 --> 01:22:54,024
The door doesn't move.
这门推不动

481
01:22:54,094 --> 01:22:55,355
How does it open?
要怎么打开它?

482
01:22:55,428 --> 01:22:57,326
I know. Leave it to me.
我知道，交给我好了

483
01:22:58,261 --> 01:23:00,124
No! Come back, Prince!
不要!快回来，王子!

484
01:23:12,262 --> 01:23:13,728
He's done it.
他成功了

485
01:23:13,795 --> 01:23:17,250
We can't leave him.
Wait here, my prince. Don't go away.
我们不能抛下他
等一下，我的王子，不要离开

486
01:23:21,462 --> 01:23:23,928
Save yourselves! Run for it!
你们自己救自己吧!快跑!

487
01:23:23,996 --> 01:23:26,689
You, too, Falkon, you great, clumsy oaf!
你也是，法拉肯，你这个笨蛋!

488
01:23:26,996 --> 01:23:29,087
Run! Run for it!
快跑!离开这里!

489
01:23:29,163 --> 01:23:31,891
I'm not leaving here without you,
my prince.
除非和你一起走，不然我不会走的
我的王子

490
01:23:33,964 --> 01:23:37,452
Give me your hand. Reach. I'll get you out.
把你手给我，伸过来，我拉你出来

491
01:24:48,001 --> 01:24:49,830
Hablok is over there.
哈勃洛克在那边

492
01:24:50,035 --> 01:24:53,001
When it's rebuilt,
you must come to visit us.
当它重建以后
你一定要来探望我们

493
01:24:53,235 --> 01:24:55,633
I'm sure to need a queen someday.
我相信有一天会需要一个皇后

494
01:24:55,702 --> 01:24:57,292
You'll find one.
你会找到一个的

495
01:24:57,535 --> 01:25:00,695
Whoever she is, Prince, choose carefully.
不论她是谁，王子，细心挑选

496
01:25:01,269 --> 01:25:05,860
I make it a rule never to take a woman
unless she can beat me in a fair fight.
我自己定了规则，终身不娶，
除非她能击败我。

497
01:25:06,436 --> 01:25:09,561
That's a challenge
I might think about someday.
这个挑战将来我或许会考虑一下

498
01:25:10,336 --> 01:25:12,131
What about right now?
现在怎么样?

499
01:25:18,404 --> 01:25:19,630
Why not?
为什么不?

500
01:25:51,705 --> 01:25:53,433
Come along, Falkon.
我们走吧，法拉肯

501
01:25:54,272 --> 01:25:55,238
Come on.
来吧


